USX Corp's USS division said it wasraising prices for all hot rolled bar and semi-finishedproducts 1100 series grades by 10 dlrs per ton effective JulyOne, 1987.    The company said the increase reflects current marketconditions.    The company could not say what percentage the increasereflects from current prices, nor could it say how much per tonthe products sell for currently. Reuter&#3;